OL,7,FJohn Kerry, the US special envoy for
OL,8,Fclimate, has said he is closely
OL,9,Fexamining the UK Government's approval
OL,10,Fof a new coal mine amid concerns that
OL,11,Fit will raise greenhouse gas emissions.
OL,13,FMr Kerry said US officials would
OL,14,Fclosely analyse ministers' claims that
OL,15,Fthe new plant in Cumbria is desperately
OL,16,Fneeded and that the coal would be lower
OL,17,Fcarbon than an alternative for
OL,18,Fsteel-making. He promised to speak out
OL,19,Fif research showed that not to be the
OL,20,Fcase.
OL,3,C'Coal is not the direction we need to
OL,4,Cmove in' warns US climate envoy as UK
OL,5,Cdefends new mine
